title: Keyboard Maestro Macros

[[Keyboard Maestro]] Macros

A couple for [[Roam]]

* "Roam Link" copies a Roam-formatted link to the current page in default browser and brings Roam to the front in Chrome
* "Roam New Daily Note" Brings Roam to front in Chrome, selects the first tab, loads the current Daily Note, and puts the cursor in the last block.

